-- Abstract surface: linear resource contract for product-relevant MULT-1 values.
-- Exact-once resources fail closed under use checks (LINEAR-EXACT-ONCE).
-- JOIN-ALG ConsumeToken is the dual algorithm on Idris side / Lean side.
