-- TYPED_IR_V0 pairs LINEAR kind with MULT-1 grades on ir_node (composes host grades).
-- Affine (at most once) is product talk (EDGE-AFFINE); not first-class on Idris public grades.
--
-- UNIT_DEEPEN_V1 exact-once consume contract (fail closed):
--   linearConsume tok  -- exact-once; second consume fails closed
--   null -> -1; already-consumed -> -2; success -> 0
--   init fails closed on id 0 (spent sentinel); live is consumability authority
-- C product symbol: slake_linear_consume (slake_linear_token *)
--
-- CONSUME_TOKEN_HOST_V0 (JOIN-ALG ConsumeToken-class freestanding host):
--   slake_consume_token          -- program state holding MULT-1 token
--   slake_consume_token_init     -- empty host
--   slake_consume_token_mint     -- mkToken shape; MULT-1; id != 0
--   slake_consume_token_consume  -- consume shape; composes slake_linear_consume
--   slake_consume_token_is_live  -- live predicate
--   slake_consume_token_check_fail_closed -- MULT-1 + FAIL_CLOSED_CHECKER_V1 path
--   slake_consume_token_host_id  -- greppable CONSUME_TOKEN_HOST_V0
-- Second consume fails closed (-2). Not residual free. Not PROVABLY.
